Output docs/media/strava-demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Width 1800
Set Height 1000
Set FontSize 20
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 0ms

Type "rd ~/Development/strava"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Down
Sleep 600ms

Type "t"
Sleep 1000ms

Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 700ms

Type "t"
Sleep 1s
